data.description: The extruder train used for printing infill material. This is used by multi-extrusion machines.
data.img_description: This model will be printed with an AA 0.4mm silver PLA core and an AA 0.8mm blue PLA core for the infill material.
data.hints: - Printing the infill with an extruder with a bigger nozzle size can increase print speed without quality loss.
